The '''Afflicted''' are [[Mort'ton local|villagers]] of [[Mort'ton]] who were cursed by [[Lord Lowerniel Vergidiyad Drakan]]'s evil gust of wind. They speak nonsense to the player if talked to.

Afflicted can be only cured temporarily by using either [[Serum 207]] or [[Serum 208]], despite the latter being a "permanent" cure, although this is for gameplay reasons.

